      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらくした頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Some time after Moon Tempest became part of the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1699.9999284,
          "startTime": 1.6999999284
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふー……やっと休憩だ～\nあ、{user}さん、お疲れ様～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Finally‚ a break~!\nAh‚ {user}-san‚ thanks for your hard work~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それは俺のセリフだよ\n最近多忙だが、大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's my line.\nYou've been really busy lately. Are you alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7333340246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "このぐらい平気だよ！\nむしろもっと頑張れるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is nothing to me!\nI might even be able to do more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6666679937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "元気が有り余ってるなら何よりだ\nでも、無理だけはしないでくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have energy to spare‚ that's great.\nBut don't push yourself too hard‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってから、沢山仕事が舞い込んできてるが\n一番大事なのは芽衣の体だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been getting a lot of work since becoming BIG4‚ but\nyour health is the most important‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.1666654507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "休みたい時はちゃんと言うから大丈夫！\nいろんなお仕事がい～っぱい出来て、凄く楽しいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be sure to tell you when I want to rest‚ so it's alright!\nI can do all sorts of jobs‚ it's really fun‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "今度新曲のMV撮影もあるでしょ？\nそれに出るまでは倒れたりしないよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and we have a music video shoot for our new song too‚ right?\nI won't collapse before that~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2666608732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "MV撮影もいいが\nその後にある、番組出演のことも忘れないでくれよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The music video shoot is good and all‚ but\ndon't forget about the TV appearance after that‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！\n月ストの特集を組んでくれるんだったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nThey're putting together a Moon Tempest special‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
